00:41:31,058 --> 00:41:32,926
Put one woman against a man
in any situation...

00:41:32,993 --> 00:41:34,828
Please.
She will outwork
the guy anytime.

00:41:34,895 --> 00:41:35,929
Girl power.
You know why?

00:41:35,996 --> 00:41:37,698
All right.
Enough, enough, enough.
(laughs)

00:41:37,764 --> 00:41:39,700
Megan, you gotta make
a call.

00:41:39,766 --> 00:41:41,702
