00:42:03,891 --> 00:42:04,825
(inhales deeply)

00:42:04,892 --> 00:42:05,826
Yes.

00:42:05,893 --> 00:42:07,628
I would--
I would think twice.

00:42:07,694 --> 00:42:09,630
I would think twice
about that final.

00:42:09,696 --> 00:42:11,064
Thank you. Thank you.
(laughs)

00:42:11,131 --> 00:42:13,066
Congratulations. Great job.

00:42:13,133 --> 00:42:14,935
You made a mistake, Megan.

00:42:15,002 --> 00:42:16,837
(chuckles)
(Kevin) All of that,

00:42:16,904 --> 00:42:18,772
and she just took the money.

00:42:18,839 --> 00:42:20,974
